{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"checkbox","title":"checkbox","subLink":null},{"id":"example","title":"Example","subLink":[]},{"id":"checkboxbaseduponchangingkeyandvaluenames","title":"Checkbox Based upon changing key and value names","subLink":[]},{"id":"inlinedisplay","title":"Inline Display","subLink":[]}],"title":"checkbox","description":"","validatorType":"validators","validationTypeTitle":"Validators","type":"simple","category":"dynamic-forms","subCategory":"controls","linkTitle":"checkbox","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class=\"title-bar\"><p>This is used to create a formControl with type checkbox to select multiple values in dynamic forms. For that you need to mention formControl name and <span class='highlighted'>source</span> which include the options you want to be selected in the <span class='highlighted'>serverData</span> and pass it in the <span class='highlighted'>formGroup</span> method of <span class='highlighted'>RxDynamicFormBuilder</span>.</p></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'example'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/checkbox/validators#example'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"checkbox-complete-component\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Next, we need to write html code.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"checkbox-complete-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-checkbox-complete\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'checkboxbaseduponchangingkeyandvaluenames'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Checkbox Based upon changing key and value names<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/checkbox/validators#checkboxbaseduponchangingkeyandvaluenames'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The name of key and value can be changed as per your requirement and they need to be passed in serverData as <span class='highlighted'>textPropName</span> and <span class='highlighted'>valuePropName</span> respectively.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"checkbox-value-component\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Next, we need to write html code.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"checkbox-value-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-checkbox-value\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'inlinedisplay'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Inline Display<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/checkbox/validators#inlinedisplay'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >If you want to group checkboxes by displaying them inline i.e. in the same horizontal line, then you can set <span class='highlighted'>inline: true</span> for that perticulare formControl in the <span class='highlighted'>serverData</span>. </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"checkbox-inline-component\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Next, we need to write html code.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"checkbox-inline-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-checkbox-inline\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}